# Browser Extension Overview

This project is a browser extension with the following key files:

*   **[manifest.json](mdc:manifest.json)**: The manifest file that defines the extension's properties and permissions.
*   **[background.js](mdc:background.js)**: Handles background tasks and events.
*   **[content.js](mdc:content.js)**: Injected into web pages to interact with the DOM.
*   **[popup.html](mdc:popup.html)** and **[popup.js](mdc:popup.js)**: Define the extension's popup UI and its logic.
*   **[options.html](mdc:options.html)** and **[options.js](mdc:options.js)**: Define the extension's options page UI and its logic.

It also includes content scripts for specific websites:

*   **[ai_studio_content.js](mdc:ai_studio_content.js)**
*   **[chatgpt_content.js](mdc:chatgpt_content.js)**
*   **[claude_content.js](mdc:claude_content.js)**
*   **[grok_content.js](mdc:grok_content.js)**
*   **[perplexity_content.js](mdc:perplexity_content.js)**
*   **[youtube_content.js](mdc:youtube_content.js)**
*   **[reddit_content.js](mdc:reddit_content.js)**

Other important files include:

*   **[styles.css](mdc:styles.css)**: Provides styling for the popup and options pages.
*   **images/**: Contains images used by the extension. (Note: Directories can't be linked directly in rules)
*   **[README.md](mdc:README.md)**: Provides a general description of the project.